name: ha719editor
description: The motivation behind developing this Chrome extension is rooted in a personal experience I had while learning AWS a few months ago. During the learning process, I encountered inconsistencies between the tutorial documents and the actual content on the web pages. For instance, the tutorial might instruct users to click on a button named 'Start,' but in reality, that button either didn't exist or had been renamed. This confusion not only affected me but also impacted other beginners.
